    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uh-Oh!</strong> It looks like the government has cloned your ridiculous yet strong-willed peanut mercenary team for evil purposes! Take them down in game modes such as Knockout, Team Nutmatch, Bomb Rush, and more. Are you ready for a NutShot? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NutShot is a free online fast-paced multiplayer peanut shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/a8670033cc45e02ab257d75b6fa810df.poster.avif?t=1763693299\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/a8670033cc45e02ab257d75b6fa810df.webm?t=1763693299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/a8670033cc45e02ab257d75b6fa810df.mp4?t=1763693299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE GANG</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/538a342e61aba8edc97775a45b308d12.avif?t=1763693299\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick between 8 different classes all with unique abilities and personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR HEAT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and find custom weapons then level them up to customize your dream gun. Want a faster fire rate, quicker reload, exploding bullets? The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY YOUR WAY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom games and change the rulesets to fit your desired playstyle, great with friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/d0e6486e9ecc7f8982eac23a180a4c42.poster.avif?t=1763693299\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/d0e6486e9ecc7f8982eac23a180a4c42.webm?t=1763693299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360950/extras/d0e6486e9ecc7f8982eac23a180a4c42.mp4?t=1763693299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLIMB THE RANKS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the ranks in all competitive game modes and make your presence known on the global leaderboards.</p>",
